{
  "stem": "6257.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't really know of anyone else, but-- but she came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was part of the underground, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was one of those official couriers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was delivering money to other people who were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- And-- so-- but then-- and also the other thing, was a terrible thing, that we saw was that the-- some of the Poles became very, very frightened.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was terribly frightening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ones who had little children who perhaps then thought that the families had all been killed, they all [INAUDIBLE] just took these children and put to them next to the ghetto wall and the Germans just shot them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Vladka ?] was also talking about how she used to try to save one of these children, but they didn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were Polish families who I suppose had offered to help these Jewish children hiding them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But suddenly, they-- they-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just-- those children just suddenly appeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw sort of one, but [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Vladka-- ?] I remember she told us that she saw more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was on the the sort of third or fourth floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yes, we were trying to pretend that we were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know if people guessed or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember some people came from-- who said they were from the [INAUDIBLE], this is the Polish underground army, to-- to-- to take some films of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was such a big-- good venue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sort of looking at the me and-- and-- and saying something, oh, it's a very risky business having these children here, to-- to the Dubils.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they obviously recognized what-- what we were, because we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
